'''藿香薊'''（學名：''{{lang|la|Ageratum conyzoides}}''）是[[菊科|菊科]][[藿香薊屬|藿香薊屬]]一種原產於美洲熱帶地區，特別是[[巴西|巴西]]的[[一年生植物|一年生]][[草本植物|草本植物]]，其頑強的生命力在其他地區常被視為[[入侵物種|入侵]][[雜草|雜草]]。[[越南语|越南语]]稱呼本物種為「豬屎草」（{{lang|vi|Cứt lợn}}），因為這種植物會在骯髒的地方生長。這種植物株高約0.5–1米，長2–6厘米、寬1-3厘米的卵形或三角形[[對生|對生]][[葉片|葉片]]，[[花|花]]為[[白色|白色]]到淺[[紫紅色|紫紅色]]<ref>{{cite web |author= |title=''Ageratum conyzoides'' |date= |work=NSW Flora Online |publisher= |url=http://plantnet.rbgsyd.nsw.gov.au/cgi-bin/NSWfl.pl?page=nswfl&lvl=sp&name=Ageratum~conyzoides |access-date=2018-12-10 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128062137/https://plantnet.rbgsyd.nsw.gov.au/cgi-bin/NSWfl.pl?page=nswfl&lvl=sp&name=Ageratum~conyzoides |dead-url=no }}</ref>或[[淺藍色|淺藍色]]{{r|producegreen}}，由多朵細小的管狀花聚生而成{{r|producegreen}}。披白色柔毛，揉碎後有異臭{{r|producegreen}}。果實為黑色線狀[[瘦果|瘦果]]{{r|hljh}}。它們喜曬[[太陽|太陽]]，長於荒地、平地和田邊比較乾燥貧脊的[[土壤|土壤]]上。

==別名==
'''霍香薊'''、'''勝紅薊'''、'''一枝香'''、'''鹹蝦花'''、'''毛麝香'''、'''蝶子草'''、'''南風草'''、'''柳仔黃'''、'''白花草'''、'''白花臭草'''、'''yumun''' (泰雅語）和'''saapan'''（排灣語）。

==應用==
{{medical}}
作為一種[[药用植物|药用植物]]，本物種在多種傳統醫療文化用作治療[[痢疾|痢疾]]及[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]<ref name="PandaLuyten2018">{{cite journal|last1=Panda|first1=Sujogya Kumar|last2=Luyten|first2=Walter|title=Antiparasitic activity in Asteraceae with special attention to ethnobotanical use by the tribes of Odisha, India|journal=Parasite|volume=25|year=2018|pages=10|issn=1776-1042|doi=10.1051/parasite/2018008|pmid=29528842|pmc=5847338|url=https://www.parasite-journal.org/articles/parasite/full_html/2018/01/parasite170135/parasite170135.html}} {{open access}}</ref>。在傳統中醫藥，藿香薊可用作治療「感冒發熱、咽喉腫痛，咯血，衄血，崩漏，脘腹疼痛，風濕痹痛」{{r|hkbu}}或治療[[中耳炎|中耳炎]]、外傷出血{{r|producegreen}}等症。
本物種亦可用作植物[[農藥|農藥]]，可毒殺[[殺蟲劑|昆蟲]]及{{tsl|en|nematicide|線蟲殺蟲劑|線蟲}}<ref name="PandaLuyten2018"/><ref>{{cite book |last=Ming |first=L.C. |chapter=''Ageratum conyzoides'': A tropical source of medicinal and agricultural products |chapterurl=http://www.hort.purdue.edu/newcrop/proceedings1999/v4-469.html |editor-first=J. |editor-last=Janick |title=Perspectives on new crops and new uses |publisher=ASHS Press |location=Alexandria VA |year=1999 |isbn=978-0961502706 |pages=469–473 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NR1IAAAAYAAJ |access-date=2018-12-10 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201021304/https://books.google.com/books?id=NR1IAAAAYAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==毒性==
本物種具[[肝毒性|肝毒性]]，不慎誤服可引致[[肝病|肝病]]及[[贅生物|贅生物]]形成<ref>{{cite journal |author=Sani, Y. |author2=Bahri, S. |title=Pathological changes in liver due to the toxicity of Ageratum conyzoides |journal=Penyakit Hewan |volume=26 |issue=48 |pages=64–70 |year=1994 |url=http://agris.fao.org/agris-search/search/display.do?f=1997/ID/ID97008.xml;ID9600846 |issn=0216-7662 |access-date=2020-09-18 |archive-date=2013-08-31 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130831151056/http://agris.fao.org/agris-search/search/display.do?f=1997/ID/ID97008.xml;ID9600846 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Fu, P.P. |author2=Yang, Y.C. |author3=Xia, Q. |author4=Chou, M.C. |author5=Cui, Y.Y. |author6=Lin G. |title=Pyrrolizidine alkaloids-tumorigenic components in Chinese herbal medicines and dietary supplements |journal=Journal of Food and Drug Analysis |volume=10 |issue=4 |pages=198–211 |year=2002 |doi= |url=http://www.fda.gov.tw/files/publish_periodical/10-4-1.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105233916/http://www.fda.gov.tw/files/publish_periodical/10-4-1.PDF |archivedate=2012-01-05 |access-date=2018-12-10 }}</ref>。[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]曾發生相關集體中毒事件，起因為穀物中混雜有本物種<ref>{{cite journal |author=Wiedenfeld, H. |title=Plants containing pyrrolizidine alkaloids: toxicity and problems. |journal=Food Additives & Contaminants: Part A |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=282–292 |year=2011 |doi=10.1080/19440049.2010.541288 |pmid=21360374 |url=https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00673672 |access-date=2018-12-10 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201021324/https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00673672 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本植物含有{{link-en|石松胺|lycopsamine}}及{{link-en|刺淩德草堿|echinatine}}{{r|hkbu}}等[[吡咯里西啶|吡咯里西啶]]{{tsl|en|pyrrolizidine alkaloids|吡咯里西啶生物鹼|生物鹼}}。

==野草風險==
在野外，本物種常會發展成[[野草|野草]]。在非洲、澳大利亞、東南亞及美國，本物種被視為入侵性野草<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hear.org/gcw/species/ageratum_conyzoides/ |title=Global Compendium of Weeds, Ageratum conyzoides (Asteraceae) |access-date=2018-12-10 |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224185757/http://www.hear.org/gcw/species/ageratum_conyzoides/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.herbarium.unc.edu/flora.htm | title = Flora of the Carolinas, Virginia, and Georgia, and Surrounding Areas | author = Alan S. Weakley | date = April 2008 | accessdate = 2018-12-10 | archive-date = 2004-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040404000539/http://www.herbarium.unc.edu/flora.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在亞洲其他稻米種植地區，本物種的泛濫被視為只有中度<ref>{{cite book |first=B.P. |last=Caton |title=A Practical Field Guide to Weeds of Rice in Asia |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ver3qCQF9EEC |year=2004 |publisher=Int. Rice Res. Inst. |pages=16–17  |isbn=978-971-22-0191-2}}</ref>，其乾草在一般農民會視為普通燃料來生火{{r|producegreen}}。

